<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.9">
<l>kulamtaruñ celvan tantiṭu maṭiyār</l>
<l>paṭutuya rāyiṉa vellām</l>
<l>nilantarañ ceyyum nīḷvicum paruḷu</l>
<l>maruḷoṭu perunila maḷikkum</l>
<l>valantarum maṟṟun tantiṭum peṟṟa tāyiṉu</l>
<l>māyiṉa ceyyum</l>
<l>nalantaruñ collai nāṟkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It grants family; it gives riches completely.</l>
<l rend="indent">All that has become the suffering that devotees feel,</l>
<l>It makes at earth level. [Then] it grants high heaven;</l>
<l rend="indent">it bestows the great land along with grace.</l>
<l>It gives strength; and it truly provides more:</l>
<l rend="indent">it even does the things of a birth mother!</l>
<l>[This] word which gives [such] good, discovered for myself</l>
<l rend="indent">- the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
